text: Aine Hoy (born 16 October 1987) is a British water polo player. She competed for Great Britain in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships. At the club level, she played for Olympic Nice Natation. == References == == Other websites == * Visa Water Polo International Day * great-britains-aine-hoy-vies-with-the-ball * london-prepares-series-international-water-polo * tock-photo/hoy-aine Category:1987 births Category:British water polo players Category:Living people
